        "richtext_cnM9KP": {
          "type": "richtext",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<p>TIMING IS EVERYTHING<br/><br/>Movement shapes us before we realize it.<br/><br/>The people who steady us.<br/>The spaces that ground us.<br/>The rhythm that carries us forward long after the moment has passed.<br/><br/>Set against the cultural energy of Texas Southern University, the A Ma Maniére x Nike Pegasus Premium reflects Black love in motion through friendship, mentorship, partnership, family, and self. A reflection on how presence is built collectively through movement, care, discipline, and intention.<br/><br/>Presented in Black and Burgundy Crush alongside Summit White and Metallic Silver, the silhouette merges considered design with Nike’s most responsive Pegasus to date. ZoomX foam, a sculpted full-length Air Zoom unit, and ReactX foam work together to create a system built for energy return, lightness, and forward progression.<br/><br/>Not simply movement for performance.<br/>Movement as connection.<br/>Movement as grounding.<br/>Movement as love carried forward.</p>",
            "text_color": "#eaeaea"
          }
        },
